snippet.title: The Scottish Parliament
snippet.description:
This is the official YouTube channel for the Scottish Parliament.

The Scottish Parliament is the devolved legislature for Scotland. It identifies and debates issues, makes law and holds the Scottish Government to account.

On this channel, you can view videos of all meetings held in the Debating Chamber and all public Committee meetings, as well as news clips, events highlights and other informative videos.

If you have any comments or questions, please contact us:

- Email: sp.info@parliament.scot
- Phone: 0131 348 5000 or 0800 092 7500
- Twitter: www.twitter.com/scotparl
- Facebook: www.facebook.com/scottishparliament
